00:03.204 --> 00:05.404
when I
was a little boy growing up

00:05.439 --> 00:10.042
here in Mississippi, I
spent a lot of time outdoors.

00:10.311 --> 00:13.912
Part of it looking
up at the night sky.

00:13.948 --> 00:18.317
We had no electricity so
the moon was the only light

00:18.352 --> 00:21.720
